x_1^4+x_1^3-x_1-Z(3)^0
gap> GeneralisedEigenvalues(GF(3), A );
[ x_1+Z(3)^0, x_1-Z(3)^0 ]
gap> GeneralisedEigenspaces(GF(3),A);
[ <vector space over GF(3), with 1 generators>, 
  <vector space over GF(3), with 3 generators> ]
